[21:0<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  &lt;avancouvering&gt; Welcome to the chat.<br>
[21:0<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  &lt;avancouvering&gt; Thank you for coming.  We'll be taking questions about the upcoming enhancement to melee classes.  If you haven't read the outline for those changes, please visit EverQuestlive.com site (specifically - <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=59510)">eqlive.station.sony.com/c...?id=59510)</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> to read up on the proposed changes.  Ask us anything you'd like about the new system or melee in general.  If we don't have time to answer them all here, we'll be recording th<br>
[21:0<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  &lt;avancouvering&gt; Please send your questions to AVanCouvering.<br>
[21:0<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  &lt;PCarrico&gt; Evening everyone. I am Paul Carrico, Assistant Lead Game Designer on EverQuest.  Or as others have known me, Frizznik the Gnome.<br>
[21:01] &lt;Hobart&gt; Hello, I am Todd Schmidt, Assistant Lead Programmer on EverQuest.  I am known has Hobart on Test Server.<br>
[21:01] &lt;jtroy&gt; Hey, I'm John Troy, Game Designer on EverQuest<br>
[21:01] &lt;Osmith&gt; Hello everyone. I'm Oliver J. Smith, the Lead Designer of EverQuest Live &amp; Expansions. Other may remember me as Valtron.<br>
[21:01] &lt;jryan&gt; Hey, I am Jamey Ryan, Lead Programmer on EverQuest.<br>
